Package ca.eshopexpress.model.dto

Class ReviewDto

java.lang.Object
ca.eshopexpress.model.dto.ReviewDto
public class ReviewDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a review for a game. Encapsulates information about a user's review, including rating, comment, creation time, and associated game and user data.
Since:
2025-05-09
